<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Activate Your Account</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Activate Your Account</h1>
  <p>Hello <%= user.name %>,</p>
  <p>Thank you for registering! To activate your account, click the button below and use the following activation code:</p>
  <h3><%= activationCode %></h3>
  <a href="<%= process.env.FRONTEND_URL %>/activate-account?token=<%= activationToken %>" style="background-color: #007bff; color: #fff; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">
    Activate Account
  </a>
  <p>If you didn't register for this account, please ignore this email.</p>
  <p>Best regards,<br>The LMS Team</p>
</body>
</html>




